snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [100] Klonoa Empire of Dreams
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Spikestuff

Klonoa: Empire of Dreams created by Namco and Now Production.
The game was released July 2001 in Japan, September 2001 in America and March 2002 for Europe (yay us)

This is a 100% clearing all Visions and well you get to read EVERYTHING just like me (only not four times).

Emperor Jillius is a dick I won't explain why but he's a dick and you should hate him.

(0:18) INTRO

(17:50) Priamill
(42:46) Jiobob
(1:04:06) Santal
(1:26:38) Leljimba
